I Mathematics Online - Platforms for Learning and Practising Mathematics (Co-Author: Emilia Wittmers) ..... 5&#13;
II Online Platforms for Practising Mathematics in German and English Speaking Countries – A Systematic Comparison ..... 13&#13;
III Reflections on the Pedagogical Potential of CBTM-Systems ..... 51&#13;
IV Pedagogical Comprehensiveness of Exercise Series ..... 71&#13;
References ..... 77&#13;
Credits ..... 81</mods:tableOfContents>
